.” 13.76. \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__III</b></Level2> (χράω (B) B), <b>lending, loan,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th c.BC: Aristoteles Philosophus “Ethica Nicomachea” 1131a4, 2nd c.BC: Polybius Historicus 31.23.4, 1st c.AD(?): Pseudo-Phocylidea 106. \">Refs 4th c.BC+</a>]","strongNumber":"G5540","accentedUnicode":"χρῆσις","relatedNos":[{"strongNumber":"G5530","matchingForm":"χράω","stepTransliteration":"chraō","gloss":"to use","_zh_tw_Gloss":"用","_es_Gloss":"usar","_zh_Gloss":"用"}],"shortDef":"use, relations, functions","mediumDef":"use, relations, functions <br /><b>use, employment, function; manner of using,</b> <ref='Rom.1.26, 27'>Rom. 1:26, 27</ref>*","stepGloss":"use","stepTransliteration":"chrēsis","count":2,"_es_Definition":"relaciones, función (en relaciones sexuales)","_zh_tw_Definition":"1) 用處, 有用 (經外含意)<br>2) 關係, 功能 (特別指性交) (羅 1:26-27)","_zh_Definition":"1) 用处, 有用 (经外含意)<br>2) 关系, 功能 (特别指性交) (罗 1:26-27)","_step_Type":"word","_vi_Definition":"cách dùng tự nhiên (quan hệ tình dục với một người phụ nữ)","_zh_tw_Gloss":"用處","_es_Gloss":"uso","_zh_Gloss":"用处"}]}